snippet.title: 5 STAGE CHALLENGE: TRY NOT TO LAUGH - The FUNNIEST VIDEO ever
snippet.description:
Here's a really fun challenge for you! Try to stay serious and hold your laugh, through all 5 STAGES! IMPOSSIBLE! Don't forget to leave your score in comments, hope it's 0! :D Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, raccoons, squirrels, kids, babies ,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
